ng throws against spells and other magical effects."},{"name":"Speak with Beasts and Plants","desc":"Orania can communicate with beasts and plants as if they shared a language."},{"name":"Tree Stride","desc":"Once on her turn, Orania can use 10 ft. of her movement to step magically into one living tree within her reach and emerge from a second living tree within 60 ft. of the first tree, appearing in an unoccupied space within 5 ft. of the second tree. Both trees must be large or bigger."}],"actions":[{"name":"Club","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +2 to hit (+6 to hit with shillelagh), reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 2 (1d4) bludgeoning damage, or 8 (1d8 + 4) bludgeoning damage with shillelagh."},{"name":"Fey Charm","desc":"Orania targets one humanoid or beast that she can see within 30 feet of her. If the target can see Orania, it must succeed on a DC 14 Wisdom saving throw or be magically charmed. The charmed creature regards Orania as a trusted friend to be heeded and protected. Although the target isn't under Orania's control, it takes Orania's requests or actions in the most favorable way it can.\nEach time Orania or its allies do anything harmful to the target, it can repeat the saving throw, ending the effect on itself on a success. Otherwise, the effect lasts 24 hours or until Orania dies, is on a different plane of existence from the target, or ends the effect as a bonus action. If a target's saving throw is successful, the target is immune to Orania's Fey Charm for the next 24 hours.\nOrania can have no more than one humanoid and up to three beasts charmed at a time."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int"},{"name":"nature","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex","note":" (ex)"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"blinded"}],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Dwarv